product_name: Casio G-Shock Gulfman Tide Digital Watch - Men's
long_description: Made with water- and rust-resistant resin, the G-shock Gulfman watch delivers accurate tide charts and an auto-light display, helping you stay on top of water levels with a simple flip of the wrist.
